ProjectLock.AlertText3: mIoU：The ratio of the intersection and union of the two sets corresponding to the true value and the predicted value of all categories.  Generally IoU≥0.5, the model effect is good, there are few missed kills, there may be overkill, it is recommended to test on the computer; IoU>0.8, the model is Excellent
ProjectLock.AlertText4: mPA: The average pixel accuracy of all categories which is the proportion of all correctly identified pixels to the labeled pixels. The higher the index, the less over-checked
ProjectLock.AlertText5: cPA: The average pixel accuracy of single category which is the proportion of all correctly identified pixels to the labeled pixels.The higher the index, the less over-checked
ProjectLock.AlertText6: IoU: The ratio of the intersection and union of the two sets corresponding to the true value and the predicted value of single category.  Generally IoU≥0.5, the model effect is good, there are few missed kills, there may be overkill, it is recommended to test on the computer; IoU>0.8, the model is Excellent
